{"tid":2245331,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"大家講下呢世人用左幾多錢落game[課金/買game]","createTime":"2020-10-16T06:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T07:39:54.000Z","uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbc416f9271cfc327446f82bbb1009c33e5c122","tid":2245331,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"講課金先<br />\n手機買過一隻幾蚊既game   課過幾十蚊，加埋唔過100蚊。<br />\n以前online game就好偶然課下(唔課玩唔落個種) 加埋無一千。<br />\n<br />\n但steam game就買左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩特價都會去買，雖然買得番黎都會玩既。但加加埋埋都幾千蚊。<br />\n以前都仲有老任啲掌機，但後尾寧願玩電腦既破解，使係機既錢多過game既錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfc8834c292b3cb3030338ba4bf1c0a77ba52ef","tid":2245331,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"玩app game抽唔齊pool不如唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfec67a35073744f52a9f0c3918154e949e1e1c","tid":2245331,"uid":117332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dfc8834c292b3cb3030338ba4bf1c0a77ba52ef","tid":2245331,"uid":1823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"玩app game抽唔齊pool不如唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"所以我而家唔多玩手機game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c952384ab59c7e31ce1e0b871f3846ce6cfa2276","tid":2245331,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:49:34.000Z","msg":"Steam:<br />\n一隻幾百蚊嘅game有10隻咁上下，其餘平果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就幾隻<br />\nPS4:<br />\n10數隻碟<br />\n課得最多嘅game:<br />\nKilling Floor 2，買槍skin都差唔多成千蚊<br />\nLoL，skin大約一千<br />\nTotal: 一萬以內<br />\n計計下都幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲要唔只得打機呢個純燒錢興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7764806ca246821ef78b83068cf3801093dbe351","tid":2245331,"uid":134103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"讀中學最多課過$2000-3000落一隻online game，每次都係課$100-200左右，課課下唔為意就課咗兩千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當發現自己為咗隻game課咗二千幾嘅時候，我先發覺課金打機一嚟係無底洞，課完其實都冇乜滿足感，二嚟我忽然之間覺得打機帶俾我嘅滿足感好空虛，轉眼即逝，其實可以用呢啲時間做其他更有意思嘅事，e.g.睇書、睇電，自此之後對打機完全喪失興趣<br />\n<br />\n嗰時講緊我冇零用錢，得午飯錢，一個月先得$700飯錢，為咗隻game搞到我幾個月都冇食過正常午飯，而家諗返起都覺得自己ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25beaa85aca4be7228fa403f5d66509ffad5c77","tid":2245331,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"細個online game+ app game課金+ ps4買碟<br />\n我估around 3-4萬到 唔太記得"},{"pid":"407caa632cfabc85d1c14a689f8fffca795dd4e2","tid":2245331,"uid":49772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:55:26.000Z","msg":"艾爾之光 - 玩咗10年 ~萬五<br />\nPAD - 6年左右 ~兩萬<br />\nSwitch/PS3/PS4/Steam ~一萬<br />\n打機其實真係好抵玩, 講緊咁多年加埋先幾萬銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他娛樂買少少嘢已經幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d94a96b0bbbaf0d7f9f20b94d6201a131d0282","tid":2245331,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7764806ca246821ef78b83068cf3801093dbe351","tid":2245331,"uid":134103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:55:11.000Z","msg":"讀中學最多課過$2000-3000落一隻online game，每次都係課$100-200左右，課課下唔為意就課咗兩千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當發現自己為咗隻game課咗二千幾嘅時候，我先發覺課金打機一嚟係無底洞，課完其實都冇乜滿足感，二嚟我忽然之間覺得打機帶俾我嘅滿足感好空虛，轉眼即逝，其實可以用呢啲時間做其他更有意思嘅事，e.g.睇書、睇電，自此之後對打機完全喪失興趣<br />\n<br />\n嗰時講緊我冇零用錢，得午飯錢，一個月先得$700飯錢，為咗隻game搞